0,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係點樣贏先？<br />\n侵略哂咁多個國家全部拎哂黎做版圖？<br />\n定淨係打到佢地投降？<br />\n我覺得會有2種完全唔同嘅可能性出現</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打贏同盟國，軸心國勝利，同盟國無條件投降<br />\n不過個世界應該一樣咁和平發展落去，只不過唔會再係由美國主導<br />\n<br />\n因為勝者為王，勝利就是正義之師</blockquote><br />\n共匪夠贏咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1146e0ea72e6f8141691bd0d0b885576a71cb55e","tid":426840,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係點樣贏先？<br />\n侵略哂咁多個國家全部拎哂黎做版圖？<br />\n定淨係打到佢地投降？<br />\n我覺得會有2種完全唔同嘅可能性出現</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打贏同盟國，軸心國勝利，同盟國無條件投降<br />\n不過個世界應該一樣咁和平發展落去，只不過唔會再係由美國主導<br />\n<br />\n因為勝者為王，勝利就是正義之師</blockquote><br />\n共匪夠贏咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德國贏, 日本唔駛投降, 中國共產黨無機會搶日本軍備, 又無左蘇聯大靠山, 邊到有資源同國民黨鬥"},{"pid":"649fcff4775f4727ace9b8cdb709e1790ab303af","tid":426840,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東南亞都變哂做日本人</blockquote><br />\n諗起都濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔止啦。當年已經打到去澳洲達爾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809228b9a2eb7f46ddcbc11babbb6702246c1841","tid":426840,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東南亞都變哂做日本人</blockquote><br />\n諗起都濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但唔會好似依家咁係禮儀之邦<br />\n可能只係一個蠻族"},{"pid":"687571f3dbb45aa6d06ed016014a58f55d3de80a","tid":426840,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"世界大同，大東亞人崛起"},{"pid":"2d9c7947f4ab82afdf696d35f3a3ddae166566aa","tid":426840,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-